| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4929 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 70b5e0ef-1af8-53e7-bb75-28b9ea17ebd7"
